OL,3,CSix stabbed in hours after Arsenal
OL,4,CPremier League victory parade
OL,6,FSix people were stabbed in the hours
OL,7,Fafter the Arsenal victory parade, the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police have confirmed,
OL,9,Fwith a total of 24 arrests during the
OL,10,Fevent.
OL,12,FThousands of Arsenal fans lined the
OL,13,Fstreets around the Emirates Stadium in
OL,14,FLondon on Sunday as the team embarked
OL,15,Fon their Premier League trophy parade.
OL,17,FThe Met deployed more than 500
OL,18,Fofficers to police the event, which
OL,19,Fsaw 10 suspects arrested on suspicion
OL,20,Fof assaulting the police, one of whom
OL,21,Fallegedly threw racist abuse.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
