FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780341072
OL,3,CSix stabbed in hours after Arsenal
OL,4,CPremier League victory parade
OL,6,FOne officer suffered a slash wound to
OL,7,Fthe hand and another was hit on the
OL,8,Fhead by an object thrown by the crowd,
OL,9,Fthe force said.
OL,11,FThe other arrests were for offences
OL,12,Fincluding sexual assault, GBH,
OL,13,Fpossession of class C drugs,
OL,14,Fpossession of a knife, being drunk and
OL,15,Fdisorderly, obstructing police,
OL,16,Faffray, and breach of a dispersal
OL,17,Forder.
OL,19,FFour police vans in Therberton Street,
OL,20,FIslington, were also left with broken
OL,21,Flights and dents.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
