OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780341072
OL,3,CSix stabbed in hours after Arsenal
OL,4,CPremier League victory parade
OL,6,FOn Sunday, London Fire Brigade warned
OL,7,Ffans not to climb on rooftops after
OL,8,Fcrews had to rescue 75 fans from
OL,9,Fplaces at a height when they got stuck.
OL,11,FIn the evening, once most of the
OL,12,Fcrowds had gone home, there were six
OL,13,Fstabbings, the Met said.
OL,15,FMost of the victims were not seriously
OL,16,Fhurt, but a man in his 20s had to be
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital in a life-
OL,18,Fthreatening condition, and has since
OL,19,Fbeen stabilised.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780341072
OL,3,CSix stabbed in hours after Arsenal
OL,4,CPremier League victory parade
OL,6,FOfficers were granted extra stop and
OL,7,Fsearch powers overnight.
OL,9,FCommander Stuart Bell, who led the
OL,10,FMet's public order operation for the
OL,11,Fparade, said: "I would like to thank
OL,12,Fthe vast majority of the hundreds of
OL,13,Fthousands of Arsenal supporters who
OL,14,Fattended the day to celebrate safely
OL,15,Fand responsibly.
OL,17,F"There was a police presence along the
OL,18,Froute throughout the event, supporting
OL,19,Fevent organisers and stewarding
OL,20,Foperations.
OL,26,@sD@OOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780341072
OL,3,CSix stabbed in hours after Arsenal
OL,4,CPremier League victory parade
OL,6,F"However, we had been clear that
OL,7,Fviolence and other criminality would
OL,8,Fnot be tolerated and unfortunately
OL,9,Fthere were pockets of anti-social
OL,10,Fbehaviour and incidents where officers
OL,11,Fneeded to intervene, including
OL,12,Fassaults on their colleagues.
OL,14,F"As the evening progressed and the
OL,15,Fmajority of the crowds made their way
OL,16,Fhome, there was sadly further
OL,17,Fviolence, including gang-related
OL,18,Fincidents.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780341072
OL,3,CSix stabbed in hours after Arsenal
OL,4,CPremier League victory parade
OL,6,F"Officers were swiftly on scene to
OL,7,Feach stabbing and investigations are
OL,8,Fongoing."
OL,10,FChief Superintendent Jason Stewart,
OL,11,Fwho leads policing in Islington, said
OL,12,Fon Monday: "This, of course, was a
OL,13,Fhuge and significant event for our
OL,14,Fcommunity and Arsenal fans more widely
OL,15,Fand we worked closely with the local
OL,16,Fauthority and other partners to plan
OL,17,Ffor the event and then throughout the
OL,18,Fday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]tD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
